title: Personal Website
description: I'm not quite sure a description is necessary... this is the website you're looking at right now!

title: Yeetcode
description: Yeetcode is a Google Chrome extension that enables two Leetcode users to battle each other. This is useful for preparing for DSA interviews and is reminiscent of chess.com's puzzle battles.

title: Earthquake Outlier DBScan
description: For CS470 Data Mining, my group sought to find earthquake outliers using the DBScan algorithm. This is particularly useful for predicting the location of future earthquakes.

title: Brain Check
description: [Current in development] Brain Check is an iOS application that enables you to see how many brain cells you've lost after hearing something idiotic. Simply click on a button and it will inform you.
